      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
