    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically superlative, having undergone full preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and structural subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, paired with a perfectly functioning variable M differential lock. The factory suspension remains tight with no bushing deflection, and the undercarriage is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. A truly turn-key specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
